The paper focuses on developing a model to find tutorial segments explaining APIs, which is a software engineering task. Therefore, cs.SE (Software Engineering) is the most likely sub-category. The model also utilizes domain-specific features and semantic similarity metrics, which are related to natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning (ML). Hence, cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are also likely sub-categories.
